c: 2
v: 197
t: "IHajji ikwiinyanga ezaziwayo nabani na ke ngoko ozimisele ukwenza iHajji makangabelani ngesondo, angenzi sono, angaxambulisani (namntu) ngokungeyomfuneko ngexesha ekwiHajji. Ke kaloku nayiphi na into elungileyo enithi niyenze, uAllâh Uyayazi. Ziphatheleni umphako wohambo, kodwa owona mphako ulungileyo bubunyulu ngoko ke yoyikani Mna, Hini na nina bantu baziingqondi"